text: 5th Avenue is a station on the BMT Broadway Line of the New York City Subway. Located at the intersection of 5th Avenue and 60th Street in Manhattan, it is served by the N, R and W trains. This station is for N, R and W trains. Behind the station is Central Park. After this station, the next stations will be 57th Street 7th Avenue and Lexington Avenue 59th Street.
